name: Εὐρυάλη
description: Euryale is the second eldest of the three mythological Gorgon sisters and means ‘the one who wanders widely’. The Re-veil collection, a collaboration between The Fabricant x Trs.Mnz, revisits the Greek myth of feminine danger and reimagines Euryale as a symbol of fearless self-expression by referencing a Renaissance French hood and streetwear cap. The piece questions their historic function as garments to hide one’s beauty. The owner will be able to wear the headpiece with a DressX code.
